Speakers Sales & Installation
HomeTech Innovations has a wide selection of speakers and sound systems for any size space, indoors or outdoors. As Eau Claire's only Authorized Klipsch Dealer & Installer, you can be assured that you're getting quality equipment that produces the very best sound. We also offer other brands to fit any price range or style. Give us a call and we'll come to your home to make the best recommendation for your application.
View all Speakers products
Check out Klipsch's wireless on-ear headphones. The Image ONE headphones are capable with Android and Apple devices and are capable of device control with the integrated buttons on the ear cup. Our prices will not be beat!





