Home Electronics & Automation Installation and Service
HomeTech Innovations is a locally owned and operated company in Eau Claire, WI that specializes in custom installation of residential and light commercial audio/visual systems. We have access to thousands of sound, lighting, and home electronics/automation products ranging from entry level to top-of-the-line. We work with your budget to insure that your audio/visual needs are achieved, whether you are building a new house or retro-fitting your existing home. With each completed job, we offer complete training and product support.

Eau Claire's only Klipsch® and ELAN® Authorized Installer
