5 Ways to Tie Lighting into the Smart Home



					
The ability to turn lights on and off from a keypad, controller, or smartphone may not sound all that essential. Once you have that type of system though, it’s downright addictive. Attaching technology to everyday tasks can turn the mundane into something super-cool. After all, asmart lighting system is convenient, energy-efficient, and kind of awesome.Forget running around the house to flip switches or worrying about whether or not the lights were left on for the entire we...		
				
